    <title>vim配置和常用命令</title>
    <link href="http://itdog.cf/2016/07/09/vim%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%92%8C%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/"/>
    <id>http://itdog.cf/2016/07/09/vim配置和常用命令/</id>
